 Benefits: 
 Generous compensation package with incentives based on performance. Benefit package includes paid group health, dental, life, and disability insurance; voluntary life insurance, vision, critical illness, and off the job accident insurance, a 401(k) plan with up to 4% match, Paid Time Off, and 10 paid company holidays. 
